title: Airbnb, Proposition F And The Shared Hypocrisy Of Bay Area Housing
description: In California, a state built on the idealism and tacit cruelty of real estate capitalism, no one is innocent. That’s no different with Airbnb and Proposition F, merely the latest of San Francisco’s Brobdingnagian sagas over land-use politics that will go down in tomorrow’s election. Read More
